{"tid":721954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那女畜牲涉虐親生小蝗蟲變植物蟲判囚15年 另綜援廢中判囚4年幾","createTime":"2018-06-29T05:45:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T08:31:01.000Z","uid":39539,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2c07369ce2010ddabbe72a37c3bda09ca81ddefb","tid":721954,"uid":39539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T05:45:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/134450_86f9c1aafd63533a6abd3d5dc15339c2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F134450_86f9c1aafd63533a6abd3d5dc15339c2.png&h=8fc111a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2015年時7歲的女童「林林」凌潤林因被疏忽照顧瘦至皮包骨，皮膚潰爛兼腦部永久受損，至今事隔三年，已經10歲的林林仍猶如植物人。其生母內地女教師早前被裁定忽略兒童罪名成立，並與無業前夫一同被裁定妨礙司法公正罪成。法官薛偉成稱林林承受嚴重的精神和肢體傷害，全由女被告所致，她亦於誤導警方調查中扮演主要角色，證據確鑿。法官指斥她大話連篇，對其惡行精心計算、冷血及惡毒，連罪成求情亦只是重申她在自辯時的版本，毫無悔意，三罪共重囚15年3個月，男被告判囚4年半。"},{"pid":"550321b7b9b7a3fc7feb9bb4314a095df7d6b613","tid":721954,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T05:47:18.000Z","msg":"天奇六年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f129e4829dd015cf2a806602a8047bc9e47a863","tid":721954,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T05:49:07.000Z","msg":"希望入面有人好好招呼佢地"},{"pid":"c3d74cfbcc560a4a2b32720a2d0f0e2e25e4844a","tid":721954,"uid":39539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T06:52:30.000Z","msg":"15年7折即係10年放監，納稅人又要養條支那女畜牲過世"},{"pid":"b2de5dd4590446dfdae0752c7d12e15eabef2ebe","tid":721954,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T07:04:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/02/011442_b6e9fbeb29f037cca097c1ed89ef88af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F02%2F011442_b6e9fbeb29f037cca097c1ed89ef88af.jpg&h=c640e90c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a28d5d1f59073ef87f2cb01a068